WEBVTT

00:03.135 --> 00:07.483
Atlantis is trending on news that the fabled lost city may have finally been found.

00:07.669 --> 00:12.081
First mentioned 2,600 years ago in accounts by the Greek philosopher Plato,...

00:12.218 --> 00:16.743
...Atlantis was a ringed city that supposedly sank into the ocean thousands of years earlier.

00:16.866 --> 00:20.216
Researchers say they've discovered its exact location in southern Spain...

00:20.283 --> 00:24.416
...by using a combination of radar, digital mapping, and underwater technology,...

00:24.524 --> 00:26.969
...and that nearby unearthed memorial cities,...

00:27.069 --> 00:30.847
...supposedly built by Atlantian refugees, helps vindicate the discovery.

